Marketing & Online Media Manager – Hospitality & Tourism Industry Exp ReqPlum Jobs – Abu Dhabi
ResponsibilitiesDevelop and implement the marketing, PR and social & digital media for the organisationResponsible for creating web content for an online portal to drive traffic and customer interactionWorking with the web development team to track SEO developmentsManage the digital marketing and social media activities of the organizationLiaising with the Marketing team to ensure that the corporate branding and marketing activities are aligned with the online strategy
Skills & Experience Required5 – 10 years’ experience of marketing & PR and social and digital marketing activities preferably in the hospitality industryExcellent communication skills – fluency in English is essentialExperience in a similar role in the GCC / MENA / Levant region would be an advantage
EducationBachelors Degree in MarketingProfessional qualifications is online marketing
Candidate ProfileAged between 30 – 35 yearsUK/European/US/Canadian/South African/Australian nationality
